  "2337860": {
    "name": "呆呆大乱斗",
    "steam_appid": 2337860,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于组队战斗的联机说明： 如果你想以小队形式加入对战，请确保所有队员都加速同一区服。 为了获得更优质的联机体验，我们强烈建议所有小队成员都使用同一款加速器。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/b5ecd6eef4547fb68a453a5ac032ad6f.avif?t=1748938117\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras_big/b5ecd6eef4547fb68a453a5ac032ad6f.avif?t=1748938117 width=800 height=185 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >呆呆战士是一群困在永无止境的竞技场里的小个子神经刀，看谁能笑到最后！4-20 名玩家可通过在线/本地联机，在俯视角快节奏 PVP 中比拼反应，赌 Buff，决出最终赢家！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/364b881e0520f3c99452cd25de65a7b7.poster.avif?t=1748938117\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/364b881e0520f3c99452cd25de65a7b7.webm?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/364b881e0520f3c99452cd25de65a7b7.mp4?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有大量奇葩皮肤与闪瞎眼的配色让你制霸战场！你的造型可能威慑全场、引领潮流、爆笑出圈，或者单纯令人忍俊不禁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/159b19416625513d17b3c9d1e1e3378a.poster.avif?t=1748938117\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/159b19416625513d17b3c9d1e1e3378a.webm?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/159b19416625513d17b3c9d1e1e3378a.mp4?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开局只有基础武器，战场搜刮才是王道！砸开宝箱升级装备，或从败者身上扒装备——反正死人又用不着！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遍布致命机关的动态竞技场殊死搏斗！地刺、熔岩与其他阴间陷阱会让你明白——其他玩家反而是最温柔的威胁… <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/c14d056e06870fe51d79da6909145735.poster.avif?t=1748938117\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/c14d056e06870fe51d79da6909145735.webm?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/c14d056e06870fe51d79da6909145735.mp4?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死亡并非终点！阵亡后你会化作承载希望、梦想、悔恨的漂浮星魂。在此形态下苟活够长，即可获得重生机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/caa13d9a1d172fc10a628482b1d9e9ce.poster.avif?t=1748938117\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/caa13d9a1d172fc10a628482b1d9e9ce.webm?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/caa13d9a1d172fc10a628482b1d9e9ce.mp4?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局五轮生死时速！每轮结束后选择被动技能：是稳扎稳打提升存活率，还是让战斗更无厘头？当然，直接选名字最沙雕的那个也行！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/5b6fcc047a904e92039a367ab136d382.poster.avif?t=1748938117\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337860/extras/5b6fcc047a904e92039a367ab136d382.webm?t=1748938117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论胜败或花式去世，康祖莫斯只在乎节目效果！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>癫狂级角色定制</strong>——让你的呆呆战士在混乱中 C 位出道！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多模式混战</strong>——单人、组队，最多 20 人同场竞技！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏对战融合轻度肉鸽成长</strong>——每局五轮急速晋级赛，打完一局就想肝通宵的魔性体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>海量武器与强化道具</strong>——威力惊人的正经武器、整活专用的抽象道具，以及…呃，一条鱼？</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>免责声明：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本游戏不自带一起玩耍的好友</strong>——请自带好友入坑，或者进行野排社交，或者…就自己享受孤独。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备迎接终极混沌——王冠唯一，适者生存！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
